'''November 22''' is the 22nd day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|12=draft}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1872|plain|1872|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|January 2|ja|1月2日|qq=|12=draft}}） – 日本の{{ill|Prefectures|ja|都道府県|qq=|12=draft}} を3府72県に再編

== Births ==
