* {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1864|plain|1864|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 20|ja|12月20日|qq=|12=draft}}） – {{ill|Takenouchi Seihō|ja|竹内栖鳳|qq=|12=draft}}, a {{ill|Painter|ja|画家|qq=|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1942|plain|1942|qq=|12=draft}})

== Deaths ==
