== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōchō|ja|弘長|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1263|plain|1263|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 24|ja|12月24日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Hojo Tokiyori|ja|北条時頼|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 5th {{ill|Shikken|ja|執権|qq=|qq=draft}} of the Kamakura shogunate (born {{ill|1227|plain|1227|qq=|qq=draft}} <ref>{{Harvnb|北条氏研究会|2001|p=280|qq=}}</ref>) * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1725|plain|1725|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|January 6|ja|1月6日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Chikamatsu Monzaemon|ja|近松門左衛門|qq=|qq=draft}}, a writer of {{ill|Joruri|ja|浄瑠璃|qq=|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Kabuki|ja|歌舞伎|qq=|qq=draft}} (born {{ill|1653|plain|1653|qq=|qq=draft}})
